Package: climateExtract
Title: Extract Climate Data From a Local NETCDF File
Version: 1.21.0
Date: 11-10-2020
Authors@R:
	c(person(given = "Reto",
					family ="Schmucki",
					email = "reto.schmucki@mail.mcgill.ca",
					role = c("aut", "cre"),
					comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3064-7553")))
Description: This is a bundle of functions that should facilitate the extraction of climate data from a NETCDF object
available from the European Climate Assessement & Datasets (ECAD; http: //www.ecad.eu/download/ensembles/download.php#datafiles) for specific time period, compute summarized values and link them to your set of spatial points.
